        <p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240); font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 18px;"><strong>一、交通</strong></span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240); font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 18px;"><strong><br></strong></span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">1、方便快捷最推荐：火车</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">自强号：约2.5小时，台北到花莲的票价是440台币（约91元人民币）</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">莒光号：约4~10个小时，台北到花莲的票价是340台币（约70元人民币）</span></span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 240); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">时间：</span></strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(0, 176, 240); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">从<span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">早上6点10分</span>开始，到<span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">晚上11点半</span>，几乎每<span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">20分钟</span>就会有一班车发出，很方便。</span></span></span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; background: white;"> </span><img src="http://7xotew.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/article-73-0.jpg" title="台北-花莲行程攻略_图片_0" alt="台北-花莲行程攻略_图片_0"></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><br></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 240); background-color: white;">出发：</span></strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; background-color: white;">台北车站。从捷运台北站M4号出口，出来就是台北火车站。火车站外观看上去还是有点旧，不过走到里面包罗万象，比较有特点。</span></span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://7xotew.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/article-73-1.jpg" title="台北-花莲行程攻略_图片_1" alt="台北-花莲行程攻略_图片_1"></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; background: white;"><br></span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">到达：</span></strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;">花莲车站。</span></span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><img src="http://7xotew.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/article-73-2.jpg" title="台北-花莲行程攻略_图片_2" alt="台北-花莲行程攻略_图片_2"></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><br></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240); font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">购票方式：</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);"><strong style="font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">1</span></strong><strong style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">、网上订票：</span></strong><br></span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">台铁网络订票有95折优惠，大陆居民需要使用英文版页面订票，订票后，会给一个“电脑代码”。凭此信用卡付款和出票。最好打印出来。</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><strong style="font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">订票时间：</span></strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">24小时运营</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><strong style="font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">订票张数：</span></strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">预约订票每人(身分证字号)每乘车日最多可预订6张乘车票，来回票可预订12张(去回程各6张)。</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><strong style="font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">订票日期：</span></strong><strong style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 240); background: white;">乘车前十四天</span></strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">开始预订，乘车当日可预订开车前一小时以上之车票。</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><strong style="font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">付款及取票期限：</span></strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">自订票日起2日内(含订票日)须完成取票或于付款网站完成付款。乘车当日订票后，须于开车前30分钟完成付款取票。</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><strong style="font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">取票地点/手续费：</span></strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">在台北火车站可使用自助取票，无手续费；在高铁人工柜台取票，也不要手续费；在711/全家等等便利店取票，要手续8元人民币的手续费。</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">台铁网上订票地址（此网站无需翻墙）：</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><a href="/fishtrip/taiwan/hualian/" style="word-wrap: break-word;" target="_blank" text="/fishtrip/taiwan/hualian/">http://taitie.taiwandao.tw/</a> </span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);"><strong style="font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">2</span></strong><strong style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">、台北火车站购票</span></strong></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">台北到花莲的火车还是比较频繁的，基本每20分钟一趟。大家可以直接到台北车站现场购买，台北车站台铁有人工窗口售票和自助售票机。可以连返程票一起买了。</span></span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);"><strong style="word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">3</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">、7-11台铁订票</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">想要购买台铁车票的朋友不用再特地到台铁车站了，只要到附近的7-11、全家、OK、莱尔富…等4家便利商店就可以直接买到对号列车的车票，不过，要付8元的手续费。</span></span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; background: white;"> </span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;"><br></span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">2</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">、飞机（不推荐）</span></strong></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;"></span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;"></span></strong></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">票价约1500~2000台币，飞行时间约40分钟，复兴航空与华信航空每天都有很多班次，出发前半小时登记，花莲机场到市中心约30分钟左右。</span></span></span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; background: white;"> </span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">3</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">、大巴+火车（有去宜兰/罗东计划的可以考虑）</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;"></span></strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;"></span></strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);"><strong style="word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;"><br></span></strong></span></span></span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);"><strong style="word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">1</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">）台北-宜兰/罗东地区（客运）</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">台北可以板桥转运站、台北转运站搭乘（葛玛兰汽车客运），还有市政政府转运站（首都客运），这几个转运站均在捷运站边排队搭车，宜兰端可以选择宜兰或罗东，如果不在宜兰停留，建议走市政府转运站到罗东，1小时可到，罗东端的客运站在罗东火车站后站门口，宜兰客运站距离宜兰火车站后站大概500米。</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><strong style="word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">葛玛兰汽车客运运营时间</span></strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">台北-宜兰：首班车早上6：20；末班车下午19：50，单程票价129台币（往返票232台币）</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">台北-罗东：首班车早上6：05；末班车晚上23：00；单程票价135台币（往返票243台币）</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">葛玛兰汽车客运官网：</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><a href="/fishtrip/taiwan/hualian/" style="word-wrap: break-word;" target="_blank" text="/fishtrip/taiwan/hualian/"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); background: white;">http://www.kamalan.com.tw/</span></a></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">首都客运官网：</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><a href="/fishtrip/taiwan/hualian/" style="word-wrap: break-word;" target="_blank" text="/fishtrip/taiwan/hualian/"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); background: white;">http://www.capital-bus.com.tw/</span></a></span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px;"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"><br></span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; line-height: 25px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">宜兰就像是</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><a href="/fishtrip/taiwan/hualian/" class="relatedlink" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; line-height: 25px; text-decoration: none !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" target="_blank" text="/fishtrip/taiwan/hualian/">台北</a><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">的后花园，少了台北都市的繁华和喧嚣，多了田园乡村的宁静和柔美。到宜兰也可赏鲸、体验飞行伞、大啖海鲜！非常适合假期休闲游。住在当地人的民宿里，感受宁静与温情。</span></span></p>
