<p style="clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://7xotew.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/article-73-20.jpg" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;" title="台北-花莲行程攻略_图片_20" alt="台北-花莲行程攻略_图片_20"></p>
<p style="clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://7xotew.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/article-73-21.jpg" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;" title="台北-花莲行程攻略_图片_21" alt="台北-花莲行程攻略_图片_21"></p>
